snippet.title: Paint Game - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a coloring book, see the sea side, and paint on everything! Featuring music by Maize Wallin! Paint game is an interactive colouring book for Mac, Windows and Linux, releasing on August 2nd, 2019!

Find out @ mjm.itch.io/paintgame

Follow Max @ https://twitter.com/ApparentRaisin

Find out more about Maize @ maizewallin.com & https://twitter.com/MaizeWallin
